#: src/cargo/running-locally.md
msgid "Running Code Locally with Cargo"
msgstr "Chạy Cargo Trong Máy Tính Của Bạn"

#: src/cargo/running-locally.md
msgid ""
"If you want to experiment with the code on your own system, then you will "
