#: src/unsafe-deep-dive/initialization/maybeuninit/zeroed-method.md
msgid ""
"“MaybeUninit<T>::zeroed() is an alternative constructor to "
"MaybeUninit<T>::uninit(). It instructs the compiler to fill the bits of T "
"with zeros.”"
